title: After Becoming SCOTUS Nominee, Judge Gorsuch Shows America Where His Heart’s at with Surprise Call To Merrick Garland

Neil Gorsuch has been making it clear to the American people that he’s the real deal. Even liberal politicians and pundits are starting to admit that he’s 100% qualified for the Supreme Court. His record speaks for itself but a lot of people have noticed the dignified way he has carried himself since the announcement […]
